sec.p:
Given a pair of gene-disease association (g, d), g and d represented a gene and a disease in the bipartite network, respectively. The cluster association score of the gene cluster corresponding to d and the disease cluster corresponding to g can be mathematically defined as follows:
1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
