				\begin{document}$$ DG\_ score\left(g,d\right)=\left(\frac{1}{\left|N(g)\right|}+\frac{1}{\left|N(d)\right|}\right)\times C\_ score\left(g,d\right) $$\end{document}DG_scoregd=1Ng+1Nd×C_scoregdFig. 5
The influence of node degree on the calculation of gene-disease association scores in the bipartite networks. The circle represented disease node, the hexagon represented gene node, the disease cluster dCluster(g) of gene g was identified by a red dotted line, the gene cluster gCluster(d) of disease d was identified by a green dotted line
